# Raw downloaded dataset content -- see data/NarrativeQA/README.md and
# data/MuSiQue/README.md for what goes here and how to get it. Keep the READMEs
# themselves tracked so the folders' purpose is documented in the repo. Git can't
# re-include a file inside an excluded *directory* (only inside an excluded pattern),
# so the directories themselves must be un-ignored before their per-file exceptions
# below can take effect -- a plain "data/" blanket rule here would silently defeat the
# "!...README.md" lines that follow, which is what happened before this comment existed.
data/*
!data/NarrativeQA/
!data/MuSiQue/
data/NarrativeQA/*
!data/NarrativeQA/README.md
data/MuSiQue/*
!data/MuSiQue/README.md